  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWe have shortened addresses in `From` and `To` columns in `Sending...` bottom sheet (looks like this `0xB4343....2B3C2`). When user taps it should copy full address value, but it just copies shortened text instead.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nFull address value copied when tap on From/To in \"Sending...\"  form\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/125253080-b3720a80-e301-11eb-9ed4-030198b58f72.mov\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status and create new account\r\n2) Navigate to Wallet \r\n3) Tap Send -> enter `0` in ETH asset editfield -> `Choose recipient` -> `enter any valid address` -> `Done` -> tap 'Next'\r\n4) Tap upon any of `From` / `To` fields\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly, release 1.15\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
